NARRATOR: <i>Welcome to the Harry Potter
Magical Movie Mode,</i>

2
00:00:06,466 --> 00:00:11,679
<i>a wondrous new way to experience</i>
Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone

3
00:00:11,763 --> 00:00:12,931
<i>As you enjoy the movie</i>

4
00:00:13,014 --> 00:00:16,476
<i>and join Harry, Ron, and Hermione
for their first year at Hogwarts,</i>

5
00:00:16,559 --> 00:00:20,438
{\an8}<i>a spell-binding collection
of fun and curious events await.</i>

6
00:00:20,522 --> 00:00:25,610
{\an8}<i>Discover filmmaking secrets and stories
from the set with director Chris Columbus.</i>

7
00:00:25,693 --> 00:00:27,570
{\an8}<i>Bewitching treats and treasures,</i>

8
00:00:27,654 --> 00:00:30,532
{\an8}<i>exploring everything from powerful charms</i>

9
00:00:30,615 --> 00:00:34,118
{\an8}<i>to fantastic foods, to mythical beasts,</i>

10
00:00:34,202 --> 00:00:36,329
<i>delight and dazzle you at every turn.</i>

11
00:00:36,955 --> 00:00:39,332
<i>And when you spy the Portkey
in the corner of the screen,</i>

12
00:00:39,958 --> 00:00:43,920
<i>you'll be transported
to an amazing deleted or extended scene.</i>

13
00:00:44,003 --> 00:00:46,005
<i>But that's only half the magic.</i>

14
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:51,844
{\an8}<i>Along the way, play the Hogwarts Trivia Challenge
